        <sect1>
            <title>Thengeld Hardradason</title>

            <para>
                Thengeld is a Brytish jarl, aged 35, tall, blonde haired.
                He is an excellent swordsman and tactician. He lives up
                in the Tanwall Hills, though comes raiding down south
                against the Rornish during the summer. About a week's
                travel away, so few Brytish near the border will know where
                he comes from.
            </para>

            <para>
                Two weeks ago he visited his brother Thorthda, and told him
                of some of his plans. He had business to attend to down in
                Rorn. Two people needed killing, according to his wizard
                Aelfgeir. Apparently Aelfgeir had a dream or something.
            </para>

            <para>
                After that business has been dealt with, he is going to
                Alstoth to meet up with Aelfgeir, and will be away for the
                rest of the winter. Freki will be handling things back home
                for him. He can't say where he's going, but it's something
                to do with wizardly things.
            </para>

            <para>
                Freki is an able administrator, though not a brilliant
                warrior. Aelfgeir's apprentice Gunhilda will also be back
                at his village.
            </para>

            <para>
                He has 30 warriors.
            </para>

