                            <age>60</age>

                            <short>
                                A Druid.
                            </short>

                            <background>
                                <para>
                                    Gellier was a Druid, based in Bryteland on
                                    the border with Tanwall. He knew some of
                                    the secrets of <e>Dragon magic</e> which
                                    he'd stolen from the Waezgaret.
                                </para>

                                <para>
                                    He lived as a hermit in a cave.
                                </para>

                                <para>
                                    Before being a Druid, Gellir was of the
                                    Waezgaret, but he went rogue and ran
                                    away. He taughter some of his secrets
                                    to the Druid Cannedd, then went west
                                    to Bryteland.
                                </para>

                                <para>
                                    He was sent a sending from Leith, with
                                    instructions on what to do. He used
                                    Aelfgeir as his tool, since it was
                                    easily at hand.
                                </para>

                                <para>
                                    Leith had him killed, since he was a
                                    powerful tool, but also loyal to her
                                    father, and she wished to destabilise
                                    her father's power base.
                                </para>
